6. Birthday:march == Food:avocado
7. Birthday:may == Sport:biathlon
8. House:cottage is in the middle
9. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the far left
10. Birthday:august is on the left or right of Food:garlic
11. Birthday:may is to the left or right of Food:carrot
12. Birthday:april == House:gothic-revival
13. Movie-Genre:animation == Birthday:december
14. Movie-Genre:zombie is to the left or right of Sport:soccer

